          v1.0 avec nous.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
          <a
            href="/pilot"
            class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full transition-all shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            Rejoindre le programme Pilote
            <span class="text-rust">‚Üí</span>
          </a>
        </div>
